<h1 id="toc0"><span>个人资料查看器</span></h1>
<div class="list-pages-box">    <div class="list-pages-item">







<div class="creditRate">
<div class="creditButtonStandalone">
<p><a class="fa fa-info" href="#u-credit-view"></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear:both;"></div>
<div id="u-credit-view">
<div class="fader">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/1" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="" style=""></iframe></p>
</div>
<div class="modalcontainer">
<div class="modalbox">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h2><span>著作信息</span></h2>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drturing" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6145045); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6145045&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610205702" alt="DrTuring" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6145045)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drturing" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6145045); return false;">DrTuring</a></span><br />
<strong>板式：</strong>由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610205702" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;">stormbreath</a></span>创建，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sekai-s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4476849); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4476849&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610205702" alt="Sekai_s" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4476849)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sekai-s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4476849); return false;">Sekai_s</a></span>搬运至中分的 “极简板式”。我并没有在该文档中使用include来调用该板式而是直接复制了css代码，因为这将允许我把网页上的Logo替换掉，还请注意。<br />
<strong>图像：</strong>该文档内使用的人像来源于<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Alan_Turing_Aged_16.jpg">维基共享资源</a></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://scpsandboxcn.wdfiles.com/local--files/drturing-s-personnel-file/DrTuring.png" style="width:300px;" alt="DrTuring.png" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>Turing博士</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>姓名：</strong>A█████ Turing<br />
<strong>性别：</strong>男<br />
<strong>基金会代号：</strong><span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drturing" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6145045); return false;">DrTuring</a></span><br />
<strong>安保许可等级：</strong>基金会本部站点及CN站点5级权限，其余站点4级权限<br />
<strong>所在部门：</strong>工程和技术服务部门[Engineering and Technical Service Department]（ET&amp;S）<br />
<strong>专长：</strong>文件与资料管理，枪械与武器，机械工程，计算机科学，密码学，量子物理学，天体物理学，生物学，心理学，模因学。<br />
<strong><a href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:%E5%B7%B4%E5%88%A5">语言水平：</a></strong>中文-N，英语-3，法语-3<br />
<strong>目前所在的基金会站点：</strong><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Area-CN-05，他偶尔会前往Site-98和Site-CN-85工作，好像还有人在Site-11，Site-15，Area-CN-42见过他</span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>鬼知道他现在在哪个站点，每天都有无数的要求他帮忙处理事故的请求，我看记录都看到眼花了。<br />
- 某不愿意透露姓名的ET&amp;S部门管理层人员</p>
</blockquote>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;当前在基金会任职的职位：</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
